- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with predicting user behavior. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper deals with textual content and user interactions. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper deals with social media and its impact on users.
